{
  "algorithm": "align",
  "comparison": "exact",
  "tolerance": 0.0001,
  "_doc": [
    "Cross-language parity fixtures for the 14 Align panel operations.",
    "",
    "Each vector specifies:",
    "  op: one of align_left / align_horizontal_center / align_right /",
    "      align_top / align_vertical_center / align_bottom /",
    "      distribute_left / distribute_horizontal_center / distribute_right /",
    "      distribute_top / distribute_vertical_center / distribute_bottom /",
    "      distribute_vertical_spacing / distribute_horizontal_spacing.",
    "  rects: list of [x, y, w, h] — axis-aligned rectangle elements.",
    "    Paths are implicit: the i-th rect has path [i].",
    "  reference: { kind: selection } or { kind: artboard, bbox: [x, y, w, h] }",
    "             or { kind: key_object, index: <i> } where i indexes into rects.",
    "  use_preview_bounds: bool; for rect-only fixtures geometric and preview",
    "    bounds are identical so this should be false in all current vectors.",
    "  explicit_gap: null or number; only consulted by the two",
    "    distribute_*_spacing ops.",
    "",
    "Expected output:",
    "  translations: sorted-by-path list of { path, dx, dy } with zero-delta",
    "    entries omitted per the identity-value rule."
  ],
